cameraOffset.title: Camera Offset
cameraOffset.description: The local space offset with respect to the target entity coordinate system

lerpAmount.title: Lerp Amount
lerpAmount.description: The amount to lerp the camera towards its desired position every frame based on a 60fps frame rate. Lerping is frame rate independent though and will be correct for other frame rates.

schema.name: key
schema.title: Key
schema.description: The keyboard key that will fire events

schema.name: keyDownEvent
schema.title: Key Down Event
schema.description: The event fired when the specified key is pressed

schema.name: keyRepeatEvent
schema.title: Key Repeat Event
schema.description: The event fired when the specified key registers a repeat press after the initial press

schema.name: keyUpEvent
schema.title: Key Up Event
schema.description: The event fired when the specified key is released

keys.title: Keys
keys.description: The set of keyboard keys that are configured to fire events

carTargetEntity.description: The entity to car spwan position

bikeTargetEntity.description: The entity to car spwan position

motionThreshold.title: Motion Threshold
motionThreshold.description: Number of meters moved in one frame before CCD is enabled

sweptSphereRadius.title: Swept Sphere Radius
sweptSphereRadius.description: This should be below the half extent of the collision volume. E.g For an object of dimensions 1 meter, try 0.2

cameraOffset.title: Camera Offset
cameraOffset.description: The local space offset with respect to the target entity coordinate system

lerpAmount.title: Lerp Amount
lerpAmount.description: The amount to lerp the camera towards its desired position every frame based on a 60fps frame rate. Lerping is frame rate independent though and will be correct for other frame rates.

raycastOffset.title: Raycast Start Offset
raycastOffset.description: Amount to offset the raycast start point from the car's center in its forward direction.

minRaycastSpeed.title: Min Raycast Speed
minRaycastSpeed.description: Minimum speed at which the forward raycast will be performed.

raycastLookAheadFactor.title: Raycast Look Ahead Factor
raycastLookAheadFactor.description: Factor to determine raycast distance based on speed (speed * factor).

minRaycastDistance.title: Min Raycast Distance
minRaycastDistance.description: Minimum distance the raycast will extend, regardless of speed.

targetBrakeSpeed.title: Target Brake Speed
targetBrakeSpeed.description: Target speed the car will be reduced to when a static obstacle is detected.
